  <h1>Feature Patterns</h1>
  <p class="lead">Feature section patterns for marketing and product pages. Showcase your product's capabilities with icon grids, alternating layouts, card-based displays, and spotlight sections.</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Feature sections highlight product capabilities and benefits. These patterns use <code>&lt;layout-grid&gt;</code> for responsive multi-column layouts and <code>&lt;layout-sidebar&gt;</code> for split content, creating engaging sections without media queries.</p>
      <p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Responsive grids with <code>layout-grid</code> and <code>data-min</code></li>
        <li>Icon integration with <code>&lt;icon-wc&gt;</code> elements</li>
        <li>Alternating layouts using CSS <code>:nth-child</code></li>
        <li>Card-based variants with hover effects</li>
        <li>Feature spotlight with bullet points</li>
        <li>No media queries required</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Icon Grid</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>A responsive grid of features with icons. Uses <code>layout-grid</code> with <code>data-min="250px"</code> to create columns that automatically adjust based on available space.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/patterns/demos/features-icon-grid.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/features-icon-grid"
      title="Icon Grid Features"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Feature grid with icons">&lt;section class="features"&gt;
  &lt;layout-center data-max-width="wide"&gt;
    &lt;layout-stack data-gap="2xl"&gt;
      &lt;div class="features-header"&gt;
        &lt;layout-stack data-gap="s"&gt;
          &lt;h2&gt;Everything you need to build faster&lt;/h2&gt;
          &lt;p class="lead"&gt;Our platform provides all the tools and features you need to ship products quickly without compromising on quality.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;layout-grid data-min="250px" data-gap="l"&gt;
        &lt;layout-stack data-gap="s"&gt;
          &lt;span class="feature-icon"&gt;
            &lt;icon-wc name="zap" size="md"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
          &lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;h3&gt;Lightning Fast&lt;/h3&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;Optimized for speed with minimal overhead. Your pages load instantly, keeping users engaged.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
        &lt;layout-stack data-gap="s"&gt;
          &lt;span class="feature-icon"&gt;
            &lt;icon-wc name="shield" size="md"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
          &lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;h3&gt;Secure by Default&lt;/h3&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;Built-in security best practices protect your data and your users without extra configuration.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
        &lt;!-- Additional features... --&gt;
      &lt;/layout-grid&gt;
    &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
  &lt;/layout-center&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Alternating Rows</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Feature rows with image and text that alternate sides. Uses <code>layout-sidebar</code> with CSS to flip the direction on even rows.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/patterns/demos/features-alternating.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/features-alternating"
      title="Alternating Features"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Alternating image/text rows">&lt;section class="features"&gt;
  &lt;layout-center data-max-width="wide"&gt;
    &lt;layout-stack data-gap="3xl"&gt;
      &lt;div class="feature-row"&gt;
        &lt;layout-sidebar data-gap="2xl" data-sidebar-width="wide" data-content-min="50"&gt;
          &lt;layout-cover data-padding="none"&gt;
            &lt;layout-stack data-gap="m"&gt;
              &lt;h2&gt;Intuitive drag-and-drop builder&lt;/h2&gt;
              &lt;p&gt;Create beautiful layouts without writing code. Our visual builder lets you design pages quickly with a library of pre-built components.&lt;/p&gt;
              &lt;a href="#" class="feature-link"&gt;
                Learn about the builder
                &lt;icon-wc name="arrow-right" size="sm"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
              &lt;/a&gt;
            &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
          &lt;/layout-cover&gt;
          &lt;figure class="feature-image" aria-label="Builder interface"&gt;
            Builder Preview
          &lt;/figure&gt;
        &lt;/layout-sidebar&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="feature-row"&gt;
        &lt;!-- Second row automatically flips via CSS --&gt;
        &lt;layout-sidebar data-gap="2xl" data-sidebar-width="wide" data-content-min="50"&gt;
          &lt;!-- Same structure, image appears on left --&gt;
        &lt;/layout-sidebar&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
  &lt;/layout-center&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;</code-block>

    <h3>Required CSS</h3>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Add this CSS to alternate the sidebar direction on even rows:</p>
    </layout-text>

    <code-block language="css" label="Alternating row styles">{alternatingRowStyles}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Card Grid</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Features displayed in bordered cards with hover effects. Uses <code>layout-grid</code> with styled card containers that respond to hover states.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/patterns/demos/features-card-grid.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/features-card-grid"
      title="Card Grid Features"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Card-based feature grid">&lt;section class="features"&gt;
  &lt;layout-center data-max-width="wide"&gt;
    &lt;layout-stack data-gap="2xl"&gt;
      &lt;div class="features-header"&gt;
        &lt;layout-stack data-gap="s"&gt;
          &lt;h2&gt;Built for modern workflows&lt;/h2&gt;
          &lt;p class="lead"&gt;Streamline your development process with features designed to help teams move faster.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;layout-grid data-min="280px" data-gap="l"&gt;
        &lt;article class="feature-card"&gt;
          &lt;layout-stack data-gap="m"&gt;
            &lt;span class="feature-icon"&gt;
              &lt;icon-wc name="zap" size="sm"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
            &lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;h3&gt;Instant Deploys&lt;/h3&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;Push to git and your site is live in seconds. Zero-config deployments with automatic rollbacks.&lt;/p&gt;
          &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
        &lt;/article&gt;
        &lt;!-- Additional cards... --&gt;
      &lt;/layout-grid&gt;
    &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
  &lt;/layout-center&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;</code-block>

    <h3>Required CSS</h3>
