  <section>
    <h2>Usage Notes</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Grid columns:</strong> Use <code>data-min="250px"</code> to <code>280px</code> for feature grids. This ensures 2-3 columns on most screens.</li>
        <li><strong>Icons:</strong> Use <code>&lt;icon-wc&gt;</code> with consistent sizing. <code>md</code> for icon grids, <code>sm</code> for card grids.</li>
        <li><strong>Alternating:</strong> Wrap each feature row in a <code>.feature-row</code> div to enable CSS-based alternation.</li>
        <li><strong>Cards:</strong> Add hover effects for interactivity. Use <code>box-shadow</code> and <code>border-color</code> transitions.</li>
        <li><strong>Images:</strong> Use placeholder <code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> elements with <code>aspect-ratio</code> for consistent sizing.</li>
        <li><strong>Checkmarks:</strong> Use <code>&lt;icon-wc name="check"&gt;</code> with <code>--color-success</code> for benefit lists.</li>
        <li><strong>Semantic markup:</strong> Use <code>&lt;article&gt;</code> for feature cards and <code>&lt;section&gt;</code> for feature groups.</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

